OL,5, Sarah Everard's killer Wayne Couzens   
OL,6, could be in line for a #7,000-a-year   
OL,7, police pension, says Mayor of London   
OL,8, Sadiq Khan - who has called for the    
OL,9, ex-officer to be stripped of the       
OL,10, benefit.                               
OL,12,FCouzens, 50, was given a whole-life    
OL,13,Fsentence for murdering Ms Everard in   
OL,14,F2021 while employed by the Met Police. 
OL,16,FMr Khan has successfully applied to    
OL,17,Fstrip Couzens of pension payments      
OL,18,Fearned while at the London force.      
OL,20,FBut he believes Couzens qualifies for  
OL,21,Fother payments due to his previous job.
